			<h2 class="entry-title heading-size-1"><a href="http://sowrey.wp/novels/the-banshee-chapter-9/">The Banshee: Chapter 9</a></h2>
		<div class="post-meta-wrapper post-meta-single post-meta-single-top">

			<ul class="post-meta">

									<li class="post-author meta-wrapper">
						<span class="meta-icon">
